| Feature               | Tech Used                  |
| --------------------- | -------------------------- |
| Product Listings      | Axios, useEffect, useState |
| Product Search/Filter | useState, Array Filters    |
| Cart                  | Redux                      |
| User Authentication   | Firebase/Auth0 (Optional)  |
| Admin Dashboard       | React + Protected Routes   |
| Payment Integration   | Razorpay / Stripe          |
| Wishlist & Orders     | LocalStorage or Firebase   |
